Class StreetViewPanoramaOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teamdev.jxmaps.MapObject
      • com.teamdev.jxmaps.StreetViewPanoramaOptions
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class StreetViewPanoramaOptions
extends MapObject
    Represents a street-view panorama object options. Contains options defining the properties of a StreetViewPanorama object.
